Uses of Package
net.markenwerk.utils.data.fetcher

  • Classes in net.markenwerk.utils.data.fetcher used by net.markenwerk.utils.data.fetcher 
    Class and Description
    AbstractBufferedFetcher
    AbstractBufferedFetcher is a sensible base implementation of Fetcher that uses a byte[] as buffer, to while copying all bytes from an InputStream to an OutputStream by sequentially reading from the InputStream into the buffer and then writing from the buffer to the OutputStream.
    AbstractFetcher
    AbstractFetcher is a sensible base implementation of Fetcher.
    Fetcher
    A Fetcher can fetch the entire content of a given InputStream into a fresh byte[] or copy it into a given OutputStream.
    FetchException
    A FetchException is a specialized IOException that indicates that a fetch operation of a Fetcher has failed.
    FetchProgressListener
